ies have the opposite\nsign from the electromagnetic and matter sources. In the gravito-Gauss law the\nsources contributed by gravitational energy and momentum-flow densities have a\nrepulsive effect on the gravitational acceleration-difference of particles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 15 Apr 2023 17:03:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-18"}
