e probable source of\nthe missing open flux. This explanation also brings in line many of the seemly\ncontradictory facts that have made resolving this problem so difficult.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 15 Apr 2023 22:35:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-18"}
